      <look> Even though you've never met one before, there is no doubt in your mind that this is a troll. He's huge, ugly, and covered in warts. Rags hang off his body, and he is carrying a large wooden club covered in studs. He's also breathing so loudly that you can hear -- and smell -- his breath from five meters away.</look>
      <poke>You step towards the troll with your hand outstretched. He roars and swings his club, almost denting the bright white wall. You decide not to touch him after all.</poke>
      <speak>The troll snarls, "You must defeat me to pass."</speak>
