      <look>The walls, floor, ceiling, pedestal -- everything is shiny, green, and smooth. It couldn't actually be carved out of a giant emerald?</look>
      <touch>They are smooth, but you can feel the imperfections, the bumps you would feel in any jewel.</touch>
      <taste>You lick the walls. There is no taste. How old are you, anyway?</taste>
      <eat>You lick the walls. There is no taste. How old are you, anyway?</eat>
      <lick>You lick the walls. There is no taste. How old are you, anyway?</lick>
      <smell>They have no odour</smell>
