  <object name="dragon">
    <inherit name="editor_room" />
    <attr name="grid_width" type="int">2</attr>
    <attr name="grid_length" type="int">2</attr>
    <alias>Secret Room</alias>
    <description>This is a small empty room -- except for the huge dragon in the middle. It's a terrifying sight, at least five times your size, with massive fangs. It snorts, and smoke drifts from its nostrils. You frantically search for the exit. There isn't one. Only you and the dragon.</description>
    <object name="dragon1">
      <inherit name="editor_object" />
      <inherit name="male" />
      <alias>dragon</alias>
      <look>The dragon is huge. It snarls at you. It seems there's no way out but to fight.</look>
      <fight type="script">
        if (Got(wooden sword)) {
          msg ("You draw your sword and charge at the dragon. He rears onto his hind legs and sends a burst of flame in your direction. You slide beneath it and drive the point of your sword into the dragon's chest. The wooden sword is not sharp enough to pierce the dragon's scales, but it roars all the same and collapses at your feet. As you stare in amazement, the dragon slowly vanishes into smoke, leaving a green medallion in its place. You pick it up and examine it: a jade medallion with a picture of a dragon. You pick it up and hang it around your neck, making a mental note that you should probably ASK someone about it later. As soon as you touch it, the room begins to fill with smoke. When it clears, you are back in the strange hallway.")
          AddToInventory (jade medallion)
          MoveObject (player, layer room)
        }
        else {
          msg ("You're not really enthusiastic about challenging a dragon with your bare hands, but there's nothing to use as a weapon. Too bad you didn't take a sword back in the training yard. For now, you ball up your fists and run at the beast. It blasts you with fire and you cringe, expecting to get burned. To your surprise, there is no heat, but when you open your eyes, you are back in the strange hallway. The gleam on the north wall has completely vanished.")
          MoveObject (north wall, banners)
          MoveObject (player, layer room)
        }
      </fight>
    </object>
